WEBVTT

00:03:58.440 --> 00:04:00.536
We will learn to read and write

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:02.576
and apply again, so what?"

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:08.000
(Applause)

00:04:09.600 --> 00:04:12.056
We started our literacy classes.

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:14.616
Every day our women would come.

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:18.375
They were so determined
that after working the whole day,

00:04:18.399 --> 00:04:21.856
they would come to the class
and learn to read and write.

00:04:21.880 --> 00:04:23.256
After five months,

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:24.816
we applied again,

00:04:24.840 --> 00:04:27.856
but this time I didn't go alone.

00:04:27.880 --> 00:04:31.240
Fifteen women accompanied me
to Reserve Bank of India.